set.seed(2)
rfor.prediction <- forecast::forecast(Women.ssa.short, groups = list(c(1:14,19)), 
                 method = "recurrent", interval = "prediction",
                 only.intervals = TRUE,

rfor.prediction <- forecast::forecast(Women.ssa.short, groups = list(c(1:14,19)), 
                 method = "recurrent", interval = "confidence",
